Special characters and symbols:
There are plenty of special characters and symbols that you can add to your banners. I could just copy them directly without using their codes:
- symbols https://www.w3schools.com/charsets/ref_utf_symbols.asp
- dingbats : https://www.w3schools.com/charsets/ref_utf_dingbats.asp
I found not of them visible in epic chats, so you need to test how they will appear in lab chat when your banner is ready.

Example: My first 3 lines banner with special characters

