Walkr HTML limitations
There are some known walkr limitations (iOS walkr versions):
- break lines are not interpreted, so if you try to use <br/> to make a new line in your banner, it won't work and <br/> will appear in the end result of your banner
- as mentioned above, <font>, <p>, <h> tags are not recognised in walkr
- css styling is also not working in my experience


